Title: Hounds of War
Description:
I think we've had enough fun on our own, yes? 

The Scarlets stationed near the city's chapel seem to be the most elite of their forces. I believe we'll find whoever is leading them there, but going alone is unnecessarily dangerous.

Time to bring the true might of Gilneas and take our city back. My forces stand ready to charge!
ObjectivesText: Open the gates to Gilneas City.
